the first songs recorded at gold star studios , at a single studio session one afternoon in july 1958 , were " come on , let 's go " , an original ( credited to valens/kuhn , keane 's real name ) , and " framed " , a leiber and stoller tune .

the cinema : the music of ritchie valens was performed by los lobos in this 1987 biography of the rock star

la bamba